Package com.upsight.android.persistence.annotation

  • Annotation Types Summary 
    Annotation Type Description
    Created
    Annotation for methods subscribed to the creation of UpsightStorableType.
    Removed
    Annotation for methods subscribed to the removal of UpsightStorableType.
    Updated
    Annotation for methods subscribed to the update of UpsightStorableType.
    UpsightStorableIdentifier
    Annotates a String class Field of a class annotated with UpsightStorableType.
    UpsightStorableType
    Annotates classes or methods to be persisted in the UpsightDataStore.
